page.title: 03TRANSPORT IN FULHAM
page.content: In 1985 buses had number routes like 220,283 & 11.These are the buses that run in Fulham.There are two types of buses,double decker and single decker.The network is run by London Transport.The buses are popular with Londons millions.The trains are very popular and very fast.Some are London Transport and some British Rail.These trains run all over London.The London underground trains are known as 'the tube'.It is very fast and one runs every 5 mins.The lines have names like District,Circle,Central,Northern & Bakerloo. Savings can be had by using the Travelcard and Buspass.
